F grant for project preparation support.</p>\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#7EBEC5\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#7EBEC5\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#7EBEC5\" image=\"http://usicef.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/step2.svg\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" module_class=\"grid5\"]\r\n\r\nThe application is evaluated by\r\nCPI, as the Program Manager,\r\nand the Advisory Committee.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#7EBEC5\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#7EBEC5\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#7EBEC5\" image=\"http://usicef.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/step3.svg\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" module_class=\"grid5\"] Upon application approval, the Program Manager engages USICEF’s network of empaneled <strong>Service Providers</strong> to provide the relevant project support. [/et_pb_blurb][et_pb_blurb admin_label=\"Blurb\" url_new_window=\"off\" use_icon=\"off\" icon_color=\"#7EBEC5\" use_circle=\"off\" circle_color=\"#7EBEC5\" use_circle_border=\"off\" circle_border_color=\"#7EBEC5\" image=\"http://usicef.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/step4.svg\" icon_placement=\"top\" animation=\"off\" background_layout=\"dark\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_icon_font_size=\"off\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\" module_class=\"grid5\"] Grant money is transferred to the <strong>Service Providers</strong> and/or <strong>Project Developer</strong> upon successful delivery of services. [/et_pb_blurb][